zm_large_yard

  Interesting zombie map for CSS. On the map there are many secrets and steam traps.
  Map works on CSS v34 and the new CSS.

  Installation: The file zm_large_yard.bsp throw on the way: D: \ games \ css \ cstrike \ maps and also in the files mapcycle, maplist, votemaplist to register the name of the map.
